# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
/target/
/gen/schemas

# iter-012 Pass #6.1: Node sidecar binary fetched at build time by
# scripts/fetch-node-sidecar.sh (~120 MB; per-platform — too large to
# commit). The .gitkeep preserves the directory.
/binaries/node-*
/binaries/*.exe

# iter-012 Pass #6.1: Next.js standalone bundle copied here by
# scripts/copy-standalone-for-tauri.mjs after `next build`. Tauri's
# bundler reads it via bundle.resources. Regenerated every build.
# 2026-05-19: copy-standalone target renamed to /resources/n/ (Windows
# MAX_PATH headroom — see windows-installer build runbook). Also ignoring
# /resources/hermes-sidecar/ which copy-hermes-sidecar-for-tauri.mjs writes.
/resources/next-server/
/resources/n/
/resources/hermes-sidecar/
